headline: VDURA Joins Ultra Ethernet Consortium to Reinvent Networking for the AI Era
summary: MILPITAS, Calif., September 30, 2025--VDURA, the company behind the world’s most powerful data platform for AI and HPC, today announced its membership in the Ultra Ethernet Consortium (UEC). By joining UEC, VDURA is extending its mission of reinventing the storage stack for the AI era into the networking domain, working with other industry leaders to ensure the fabric of tomorrow’s infrastructure keeps pace with the explosive demands of AI and HPC.
